Mouse : <Button> : Any Mouse Button with mouse ptr over the widget
        <Button-1> : Left Mouse Button
        <Button-2> : Middle Mouse Button
        <Button-3> : Right Mouse Button
        <Button-4> : Scroll up if Wheel support
        <Button-5> : Scroll down if Wheel support
        <ButtonPress-1>
        <ButtonPress-2>
        <ButtonPress-3>
        <ButtonRelease-1>
        <ButtonRelease-2>
        <ButtonRelease-3>
        <B1-Motion>
        <B2-Motion>
        <B3-Motion>
        <Double-Button-1>
        <Double-Button-2>
        <Double-Button-3> : can also use Triple as Prefix


Listbox : <<ListboxSelect>>

Widget : <Configure> : event.width event.height new dimensions
         <Enter> :  Widget Entered (n Enter Key)
         <Leave> :  Widget Left (n Enter Key)

KeyBoard :  <Key> : event.char in callback
            <Return>
            <FocusIn>
            <focusOut>
            <Alt_L>
            <Control_L>
            <Shift_L>
            <F1>
            <Up>
            <Escape>
            <Backspace>
            <Caps_Lock>
            <Shift-Up>
            <Prior> : Pg Up
            <Next> : Pg Dwn
            <space>
            <less>
            <Num_Lock>
            'a' or '1': Printable Characters like (a,b,c,d,----) (1,2,3,4,------)


